Quite apart from making a fool of himself with his incoherent political statements on social media, Edward is becoming a real embarrassment to his profession - law. There is nothing wrong with him defending his father, if he feels No1 is being unfairly criticised. But to do so by throwing mud at people is a sign of immaturity. Mathews Phosa is no paragon of virtue, but what does calling him a sellout make your dad, Edward?